Wednesday, April 1, 1998

MERIT DOCKET

97-2394. Workman v. Carter.

In Habeas Corpus. . On return of writ, motion to strike Exhibit D to respondent’s return of writ, and supplemental return of writ. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
